39:41.913 --> 39:44.550
Perhaps I did see them.

39:44.583 --> 39:46.785
Perhaps I do not recall.

39:46.818 --> 39:48.587
- That's not what
you said last time.

39:48.620 --> 39:50.456
- Well, we have
