39:57.596 --> 39:59.965
There is no touching at all.

39:59.998 --> 40:01.633
You're aware of that, correct?

40:02.634 --> 40:04.536
- Get off of me!

40:04.570 --> 40:06.538
- I know what I know.

40:06.572 --> 40:08.474
And I share what I share.

40:08.507 --> 40:11.743
- Just answer the
fuckin' question.

40:11.777 --> 40:14.546
- I see someone
has anger issues.

40:15.647 --> 40:18.550
I live by the family rule.

40:18.584 --> 40:21.152
Each year when the
hallowed spirit is new,

40:21.186 --> 40:24.189
each year to thine
own self be true.

40:25.591 --> 40:27.493
- Family rule?

40:27.526 --> 40:28.827
- Can you explain?

40:30.762 --> 40:34.933
- We were a traveling circus
and really quite styled,

40:36.067 --> 40:39.505
till my mother died
giving birth to a child.

40:39.538 --> 40:44.142
The show became raw and
was shut down by the law

40:44.175 --> 40:47.746
for questionable reasons
still yet unfiled.

40:48.947 --> 40:51.883
So we moved to a town,
and we tried to fit in,

40:51.917 --> 40:54.820
until my father
committed that sin.

40:55.954 --> 40:59.691
So the sibling gathered
in a room for din

40:59.725 --> 41:03.629
and decided our family
would travel again.

41:03.662 --> 41:05.664
- Getting more interesting.

41:05.697 --> 41:08.767
- So after the
schoolhouse killings,

41:08.800 --> 41:11.670
your family went
back out on the road?

41:11.703 --> 41:15.240
- Don't believe everything
you hear, Detective,

41:15.273 --> 41:18.544
and only half of what you see.

41:18.577 --> 41:19.578
- Moving on.

41:20.512 --> 41:24.683
The seven teens are
shown climbing a ladder.

41:24.716 --> 41:27.185
Where does that
ladder lead, any idea?

41:27.218 --> 41:28.319
- I do not recall.

41:30.121 --> 41:32.591
- You have no idea where this
ladder might lead visitors

41:32.624 --> 41:33.592
to the Haunted Maze?

41:33.625 --> 41:34.560
- Nope.

41:34.593 --> 41:35.694
- We went back to the barn.

41:35.727 --> 41:37.729
The ladder's
nowhere to be found.

41:37.763 --> 41:38.964
So it just vanished?

41:38.997 --> 41:40.566
- Perhaps it did.

41:40.599 --> 41:42.634
Perhaps it did not.

41:42.668 --> 41:43.869
- Can you share with us

41:43.902 --> 41:44.870
where the teens may
have been located

41:44.903 --> 41:46.738
in the barn, overnight?

41:46.772 --> 41:47.706
- The barn?

41:49.340 --> 41:51.309
- Your traveling entourage,

41:51.342 --> 41:53.579
park an RV on the property

41:53.612 --> 41:55.681
where you're gonna set
the festival, correct?

41:55.714 --> 41:58.850
- I believe that is the
case in most of our setups.

41:58.884 --> 42:00.952
- Who resided in the RV?

42:00.986 --> 42:03.154
- The traveling entourage.

42:04.990 --> 42:08.560
- Who was there the
evening of October 31st?

42:08.594 --> 42:10.095
- I do not recall.

42:11.997 --> 42:13.832
- Let me share this with you.

42:13.865 --> 42:15.967
Next time the teens are seen,

42:16.001 --> 42:20.305
they're running into
the barn at 5:14 a.m.

42:20.338 --> 42:24.710
A.M., so they were there
overnight and are still alive.

42:27.779 --> 42:28.980
The teens' minivan never left

42:29.014 --> 42:31.750
the Halloween festival property.

42:31.783 --> 42:36.121
As you see, we have you on
camera chasing the seven teens.

42:41.793 --> 42:44.663
- Is this funny to you, Clancy?

42:44.696 --> 42:46.197
- Pesky teenagers.

42:47.966 --> 42:49.801
What you think is fact

42:51.069 --> 42:52.638
is, in fact, false.

43:03.114 --> 43:04.850
- Let us out!

43:04.883 --> 43:06.685
- My God, is this a snake?

43:06.718 --> 43:07.986
Okay.

43:08.019 --> 43:09.655
- That was metal.

43:10.656 --> 43:11.256
