43:36.982 --> 43:39.417
- Okay, eight.

43:39.450 --> 43:40.952
- Seven.

43:40.986 --> 43:42.087
- One.

43:42.120 --> 43:43.221
- Two.

43:43.254 --> 43:44.656
- Nine.

43:44.690 --> 43:45.423
- 10.

43:45.456 --> 43:47.025
Well, Maci wins it with eight.

43:47.058 --> 43:48.827
- Oh dude, she wins!

43:48.860 --> 43:50.829
- Okay, I've got one.

43:50.862 --> 43:53.799
What if we're all stranded
in this haunted house

43:53.832 --> 43:57.402
with psychos, and you
have this one chance

43:57.435 --> 44:00.271
to say goodbye to
all your friends,

44:00.305 --> 44:02.140
what would you say?

44:02.173 --> 44:04.209
- I love you all.

44:04.242 --> 44:05.777
Don't forget me.

44:09.480 --> 44:13.284
- I would just tell everyone
come fuckin' find me!

44:13.318 --> 44:15.821
- You guys, I'm serious.

44:15.854 --> 44:18.924
I have this really horrible
feeling in the pit of my stomach

44:18.957 --> 44:21.693
that something bad
is gonna happen.

44:21.727 --> 44:23.461
I know we're just
here until tomorrow,

44:23.494 --> 44:26.765
but this feeling
is gut-wrenching.

44:26.798 --> 44:27.699
I mean, this is freaky.

44:27.733 --> 44:29.968
None of our phones are working.

44:30.001 --> 44:32.871
It's like the power has
been jammed or something.

44:32.904 --> 44:36.875
I mean, is anybody's phone
working at all, anyone's?

44:38.276 --> 44:40.011
- No, I have nothing.

44:41.446 --> 44:43.749
- Mine shut off.

44:46.284 --> 44:49.087
- Can anyone hear
us, anyone out there?

44:49.120 --> 44:51.089
- Come on, this
isn't fucking right.

44:51.122 --> 44:53.291
- We're in here!
- It's wrong!

44:57.796 --> 44:59.230
- Let us
go here, come on!

45:03.234 --> 45:05.303
- You got my money.

45:05.336 --> 45:07.472
- Come
on, it's not cool.

45:07.505 --> 45:08.907
- Hello?

45:10.008 --> 45:10.842
Hello!

45:25.791 --> 45:27.725
- Let us go!

45:31.863 --> 45:32.463
- Well, hello.

45:32.497 --> 45:33.298
- Hello.

45:33.331 --> 45:34.766
I'm Agent Hawk.

45:34.800 --> 45:36.334
- What brings you out here?

45:36.367 --> 45:37.969
- Oh I've been following
Clancy the Clown

45:38.003 --> 45:39.905
and his entourage
since Chicago, Illinois

45:39.938 --> 45:41.372
on a narcotics tip.

45:41.406 --> 45:43.241
- Yeah, well, those carnies
are pretty weird people.

45:43.274 --> 45:44.209
- Indeed.

45:44.242 --> 45:45.043
So I was just curious.

45:45.076 --> 45:46.311
What's your status here?

45:46.344 --> 45:47.378
- Well, let me tell
you what's going on.

47:20.505 --> 47:24.275
- So Clancy has more
kids locked in the barn.

47:26.011 --> 47:27.412
- Again?

47:27.445 --> 47:28.246
- Again.

47:46.932 --> 47:47.899
- Yeah?

47:47.933 --> 47:50.635
- Hi, I'm Officer O'Doyle,
and this here is--

47:50.668 --> 47:51.970
- Agent Hawk.

47:52.971 --> 47:54.005
- What do you want?

47:54.039 --> 47:55.907
- We just need to ask you
a couple of questions.

47:55.941 --> 47:56.541
- What?

47:56.574 --> 47:57.943
- Who is that?

47:57.976 --> 47:59.144
- It's the po-pos.

47:59.177 --> 48:01.913
They have some
questions for you.

48:01.947 --> 48:03.114
- Is this your property?

48:03.148 --> 48:05.583
- Nah, we just
hold up shop here.

48:05.616 --> 48:07.652
- For the traveling carnival.

48:07.685 --> 48:10.121
- I noticed a minivan
in the parking lot.

48:10.155 --> 48:11.556
It belongs to a
couple of teenagers

48:11.589 --> 48:12.958
who have been missing
all night long,

48:12.991 --> 48:14.025
and their parents
wanted us to come out

48:14.059 --> 48:16.928
and check around for them.

48:16.962 --> 48:19.197
- Well, what's that
got to do with us?

48:19.230 --> 48:21.099
- Yeah, who are you here to see?

48:21.132 --> 48:23.634
- Agent Hawk, want to come in?

48:25.003 --> 48:27.005
- Have any of you
ladies seen a group

48:27.038 --> 48:29.407
of teenagers, around closing?

48:29.440 --> 48:31.542
- Not at closing.

48:31.576 --> 48:32.978
Well, if you don't mind,

48:33.011 --> 48:35.246
we'd like to take look
around the grounds.

48:35.280 --> 48:36.948
- It'll cost you.

48:36.982 --> 48:39.050
- Ca-ching!

48:39.084 --> 48:42.453
- I handle the money
in this entourage.

48:42.487 --> 48:43.521
- No, you don't.

48:43.554 --> 48:44.655
- Yeah, I does.

48:44.689 --> 48:45.556
- No, you don't.

48:45.590 --> 48:47.092
- Yeah, I does!

48:47.125 --> 48:48.593
- No, you don't!
- Yeah!

48:48.626 --> 48:50.595
- We're just gonna take
a look around then, okay?

48:50.628 --> 48:52.230
- Blah, blah, blah.

48:59.637 --> 49:01.272
- You should go now.

49:11.049 --> 49:13.418
- I had Officer Trent check
the carnival rides already,

49:13.451 --> 49:15.120
so I'll go ahead, and
I'll check the back barn.

49:15.153 --> 49:16.054
- I'll check the front one.

49:16.087 --> 49:17.222
- Alrighty, let's go.

50:25.423 --> 50:26.257
- Hello?

50:38.336 --> 50:39.170
Hello?

50:40.571 --> 50:42.006
Is anybody there?

52:17.368 --> 52:18.269
Look what I found?

52:18.303 --> 52:19.304
- Cute.

52:19.337 --> 52:20.238
- Yeah.

52:20.271 --> 52:21.239
Did you find anything?

52:21.272 --> 52:22.573
- Nah.

52:22.607 --> 52:24.275
- I haven't seen
anything either.

52:24.309 --> 52:26.211
- Let's go check behind
the barn, you know,

52:26.244 --> 52:27.345
the parking lot,

52:27.378 --> 52:29.347
all good.
- Got it, got it.

52:48.999 --> 52:51.836
- Hey,
someone out there!

52:54.272 --> 52:56.274
Guys, let us out!

52:56.307 --> 52:57.308
We're stuck in here!

52:57.342 --> 52:59.377
- We've got hard.
- Let us out!

52:59.410 --> 53:00.545
- I'm just
holding, come on!

53:00.578 --> 53:01.746
- You locked us in!

53:12.890 --> 53:14.825
- Officer Trent here.

53:14.859 --> 53:15.960
The Landers' minivan was there,

53:15.993 --> 53:18.863
but we took around the festival
property and the barns.

53:18.896 --> 53:20.531
We didn't see 'em.

53:20.565 --> 53:22.500
- We also spoke with a couple
of the carnival workers,

53:22.533 --> 53:26.471
and they hadn't seen anyone
at closing time, either.

53:26.504 --> 53:27.305
- Orders
from the chief are

53:27.338 --> 53:29.307
for you to stay put.

53:29.340 --> 53:32.009
The Landers are on their way.

53:32.042 --> 53:33.344
- We just left there.

53:33.378 --> 53:34.745
We searched the entire property.

53:34.779 --> 53:36.714
No one's there.

53:36.747 --> 53:38.616
I'm bettin' the kids took
off with another friend,

53:38.649 --> 53:41.252
and they're havin'
themselves a good time.

53:41.286 --> 53:42.420
You know what I mean?

53:42.453 --> 53:46.424
- Oh, but I need
you to get back out there.

53:46.457 --> 53:49.327
Report in when back-up arrives.

53:49.360 --> 53:50.395
- Back-up?

53:51.796 --> 53:53.331
- We hear you, partner.

53:53.364 --> 53:56.367
- Not another word,
we're on our way.

53:59.537 --> 54:01.639
- Hey!
- We're ready to go now.

54:01.672 --> 54:04.275
- Open the door!

54:04.309 --> 54:06.544
- Please, somebody.

54:12.583 --> 54:14.319
- Well, I got orders
from Chief Harrison.

54:14.352 --> 54:16.321
They're for us to stay here
at the festival grounds

54:16.354 --> 54:17.588
and for you--

54:17.622 --> 54:18.789
- I'm supposed to
be home right now.

54:18.823 --> 54:20.391
The sun is comin' up.

54:20.425 --> 54:22.593
- And for you, Officer Trent,

54:22.627 --> 54:24.529
you're to take my
car, go into town

54:24.562 --> 54:26.631
and check out a call
that came in earlier

54:26.664 --> 54:29.700
about a girl who was wandering
in a field near Main Street.

54:29.734 --> 54:31.936
The chief said that the Landers
family will be here soon,

54:31.969 --> 54:32.970
so hurry back.

54:33.003 --> 54:33.804
- You got it.

54:41.045 --> 54:42.513
- Looks like you're pullin'
double duty there, O'Doyle.

54:42.547 --> 54:43.381
- Thanks.

54:58.463 --> 54:59.497
- Turn on the car
and warm it up a bit.

54:59.530 --> 55:00.565
- Sure thing.
- It's cold.

55:00.598 --> 55:01.399
- It's freezing in here.

55:04.469 --> 55:05.803
Oh shit!

55:05.836 --> 55:06.737
What the hell?

55:06.771 --> 55:08.439
- That was priceless.

55:08.473 --> 55:09.073
- Nice.

55:09.106 --> 55:09.907
- Oh.

55:09.940 --> 55:11.376
- Damn clown.

55:41.472 --> 55:42.440
- What was that?

55:42.473 --> 55:45.042
- Yeah, what was that?

55:49.514 --> 55:50.448
- Shit, my heels!

56:04.462 --> 56:08.633
- Your fingerprints were found
on this young female's body.

56:10.501 --> 56:13.538
Unless you can explain
or unless you know

56:13.571 --> 56:16.541
who's behind these
killings, if it was one

56:16.574 --> 56:18.843
of your younger sisters
or another worker,

56:18.876 --> 56:20.478
we can work out a deal for you.

56:20.511 --> 56:23.848
- Or prison is calling
your name for life.

56:23.881 --> 56:26.584
- That tape only
proves the teens were

56:26.617 --> 56:30.588
at the haunted facility,
camping out for some alone time.

56:33.824 --> 56:37.662
And the fingerprints you
have, ever so divine,

56:39.530 --> 56:42.433
you are well aware
are not of mine.

56:45.603 --> 56:49.574
Thanks for playing.

56:51.676 --> 56:53.077
- Detective Cole?

56:54.244 --> 56:56.046
Can I have a word with you?

56:56.080 --> 56:57.014
- Yes, sir.

57:06.791 --> 57:09.527
- You ever been to prison?

57:09.560 --> 57:12.863
If you take a shower,
don't drop the soap.

57:13.864 --> 57:16.467
They will butt-fuck you.

57:16.501 --> 57:19.537
You sure you want
to go there, hmm?

57:19.570 --> 57:21.939
Oh boy, they'll have
a lot of fun with you.

57:21.972 --> 57:23.674
They like make-up.

57:24.609 --> 57:26.076
- Sounds intriguing.

57:27.845 --> 57:29.514
- Oh it is, yeah.

57:29.547 --> 57:31.482
Okay, without a doubt,

57:31.516 --> 57:33.150
without a doubt.

57:33.183 --> 57:35.486
Oh they'd love you,

57:35.520 --> 57:37.655
that long, pretty hair.

57:38.656 --> 57:40.925
Yeah, I'd like to be there.

57:40.958 --> 57:43.494
Unfortunately, I got a date.

58:59.937 --> 59:01.606
- What the hell's
going in there?

59:01.639 --> 59:02.773
- Well, before his lawyer
arrives, we need to get

59:02.807 --> 59:06.677
to the bottom of where the
teens might be or a confession.

59:06.711 --> 59:08.145
- Oh, I get that,

59:08.178 --> 59:10.748
but you do realize that
you just threw down

59:10.781 --> 59:13.584
on the table information
he already has.

59:13.618 --> 59:15.252
We just confirmed that
we don't know anything

59:15.285 --> 59:16.721
about those teenagers.

59:16.754 --> 59:17.822
- Sir, I know I took
a stab in the dark.

59:17.855 --> 59:20.758
However, I might be spot
on with this information.

59:20.791 --> 59:23.728
- Might be spot
on doesn't cut it.

59:23.761 --> 59:25.963
The sociopathic mind,
the way it works,

59:25.996 --> 59:30.000
the girl in the picture
you showed him is alive.

59:30.034 --> 59:31.736
Clancy knows this.

59:33.771 --> 59:36.607
- We gave him too
much information.

59:36.641 --> 59:39.910
I know I, I saw his
facial expression

59:39.944 --> 59:41.278
the second we threw
the picture down

59:41.311 --> 59:44.715
on the table saying his
fingerprints were on it.

59:44.749 --> 59:46.150
Dammit.

